### 장바구니 항목 추가 (비회원/회원)
POST http://localhost:10236/api/customers/carts/items
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": 1,
  "productId": 1,
  "quantity": 2
}

### 장바구니 항목 수량 수정 (비회원/회원)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/customers/carts/items/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quantity": 5
}

### 장바구니 항목 삭제 (비회원/회원)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/customers/carts/items/1
Content-Type: application/json

### 고객 장바구니 항목 조회 (페이징 처리)
GET http://localhost:10236/api/customers/1/carts?page=0&size=5
Accept: application/json


